                <h3 class="heading-primary"><strong>Who</strong> We Are</h3>
                <p>We are a team of passionate entrepreneurs who believe in improving the world with technology. During
                    the deacde of 2010, each year approximately 150 million laptops are sold across the world. This
                    means that every year 150 million laptops will go to landfills. While people think e-waste, we
                    believe this is an opportunity for us to improve lives of 150 million people who cant afford new
                    laptops. We believe that we can help mother earth by reusing these old laptops.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Today the reused laptop segment is fragmented where there are multiple brochures who add cost to the
                    reusable ewaste there by increasing cost to the end user. This harms the whole business as the new
                    laptops can compete with old used laptops in pricing. If we can remove the unnecessary in
                    efficiencies in the system and get more money in recyclers hands and the end customer, this could be
                    a win-win situation. It will also ensure that this trade is not threatened by the new laptops. We
                    think together we can make a difference.
                </p>
